    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved=2 vs. required=3) is accepted because the static compression-bending COU is deterministic and the single F1717 test condition is fully representative of the intended use. Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk level with Medium decision consequence. Package accepted with documented acknowledgment of the Test conditions gap.",
